<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color:#f4f6f9; padding:20px;">

<table align="center" width="600" style="background:white; border-radius:8px; padding:30px; box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

<tr>
<td style="text-align:center; padding-bottom:20px;">
<h2 style="color:#1B5297;">TalentForce Recruitment</h2>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="font-size:16px; color:#333;">
Hello <b>{!Contact.FirstName}</b>,
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding-top:15px; font-size:15px;">
Your interviews for the position <b>{!Opportunity.Name}</b> have been scheduled.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding-top:25px;">

<table width="100%" style="border-collapse:collapse;">

<tr style="background:#eef3fb;">
<td style="padding:12px;"><b>HR Interview</b></td>
<td style="padding:12px;">{!HR_Start}</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding:12px;"><b>Technical Interview</b></td>
<td style="padding:12px;">{!TECH_Start}</td>
</tr>

<tr style="background:#eef3fb;">
<td style="padding:12px;"><b>Manager Interview</b></td>
<td style="padding:12px;">{!MGR_Start}</td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding-top:25px; font-size:14px;">
Please confirm your availability.
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td style="padding-top:30px; font-size:14px;">
Best regards,<br>
<b>TalentForce Recruitment Team</b>
</td>
</tr>

</table>

</body>
</html>